aVand the Nobel Prize awarded to
p191
aVRichard Axel and Linda Buck
p192
aVwas only awarded in 2004
p193
aVfor their discovery of how smell works.
p194
aVIt's really hard,
p195
aVbut in essence, nerves from the brain
p196
aVgo up into the nose
p197
aVand on these nerves exposed in the nose
p198
aVto the outside air are receptors,
